[SPEAKER NOTE: So how does UMOJA-ai actually work? There are six core components. First, an AI-powered avatar delivers lessons that are fully aligned to the national curriculum. Second, the classroom teacher controls the pace \u8212\'97 this is not a replacement for teachers, it is an amplification of their capability. Third, the hardware is a low-cost ruggedized tablet with a pico projector \u8212\'97 purpose-built and locked to the UMOJA system. Fourth, everything runs on a solar-powered battery, eliminating dependency on grid electricity. Fifth, content streams over the mobile telecom network using zero-rated data. And sixth, where there is no network coverage at all, the system runs entirely offline, updated monthly. Let me stress: we empower teachers. We do not replace them.]}
